      "title": "为 Balance Heater 添加出口温度目标占位符",
      "target": {
        "type": "unit",
        "id": "heater-4"
      },
      "rationale": "诊断指出该加热器单元启用了 outlet_temperature 控制模式，但未提供具体的温度目标值。提供对应参数占位符可修正 UNIT_PARAMETER_INCOMPLETE 错误。",
      "patch": {
        "parameter_placeholders": [
          {
            "name": "outlet_temperature_target"
          }
        ]
